&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelors Degree or higher in scientific/healthcare/business field&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience (7+ years) in clinical research and project management within the pharmaceutical industry (Biotech/small pharma experience preferred).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in rare disease and/or liver disease is a plus.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
